谷禪師的一番教導，使得他頓悟。於是，他立志改變自己的命運，不但考取了進士，而且還有了兩個兒子，活到了74歲。<br />\n<br />\n這正如《了凡四訓》所講：有志於功名者，必得功名；有志於富貴者，必得富貴。人之有志，如樹之有根，立定此志，須念念謙虛，塵塵方便，自然感動天地，而造福由我。"},{"pid":"46b05ce63cd7bee87298bf3b26e4b3b5f00f805f","tid":1659031,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"細你4年  同你同一日生日<br />\n八字唔係計西曆 你諗多左"},{"pid":"c07167cf8954ba755bbd0c09bb2f145ac0d3a45f","tid":1659031,"uid":128969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff7f178d41a87890b7faa1655a4f38f338742bb1","tid":1659031,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老實講你咁垃圾耶蘇都改唔到你條命 你已經完美解釋左點解會咁"},{"pid":"2648d6e99873132b7fd0ce0cb3db769f5cb70840","tid":1659031,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422216fc5da5c21ffa87b6a107c85e8e27fa27ef","tid":1659031,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNErDT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNErDT0.png&h=67c311a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"一黎你九幾年，以及幾點出世，睇下你係注定一般定真係好命又奇怪地冇。<br />\n二黎冇可能換命。玩法科可以做低你可以做高你，但無聽過話用你既運氣同人地既運氣對調，況且有十幾個其他選擇既情況下冇人會用啲咁既手段。"},{"pid":"9bcfaafc9f3d8f561c54854415eb3715e2e84792","tid":1659031,"uid":71726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"On9 人生一定有起跌<br />\n就算你條命底係誠哥就一定冇煩惱一凡風順咩"},{"pid":"dc293e4ed50e5e04d148cdff989297ce221b28ba","tid":1659031,"uid":333427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"之前都有宗教人士話我會入U，所以我走咗去讀asso，但淨得Ou，痕大，cie自資學士肯比offer我。